Description: Provides convenient access to data extracted from
  some of the spreadsheet files made available by the chemical hazards database
  of the European Food Safety Authority (EFSA), accessible via
  <https://www.efsa.europa.eu/en/data-report/chemical-hazards-database-openfoodtox>.
